<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ر غ د:</span> عِيشَةٌ <span class="c2">(رَغْدٌ)</span> بِوَزْنِ فَلْسٍ وَ <span class="c2">(رَغَدٌ)</span> بِوَزْنِ فَرَسٍ أَيْ وَاسِعَةٌ طَيِّبَةٌ، وَبَابُهُ طَرِبَ وَظَرُفَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>